Type: Package
Title: Model-Based Detection of Disease Clusters
Version: 1.0-1
Encoding: UTF-8
Date: 2020-02-21
Author: Virgilio Gomez-Rubio, Paula Esther Moraga Serrano, Barry
    Rowlingson
